# Keep the Docker build context tiny. The MaskFactory repo root contains huge
# governed trees (data/ junction -> F: ~251 GiB, models/, MaskedWarehouse/,
# runtime_artifacts/, cvat/, qa/). The serve/train images only need pyproject,
# src/, and docker/. Ignore everything, then re-include the needed paths.
*

!pyproject.toml
!README.md
!src/
!docker/
!deploy/
!deploy/runpod_serverless/
!deploy/runpod_serverless/**

# Even within re-included trees, drop caches/build noise.
**/__pycache__/
**/*.pyc
**/*.pyo
**/*.egg-info/
